spec_data.Name: perl-Mojolicious-Plugin-RenderFile
spec_data.Description:
Mojolicious::Plugin::RenderFile is a Mojolicious plugin that makes it
easy to provide files for download. It also allows customization of
the HTTP headers sent to the client.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 28 Jul 2017 01:33:26 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Mojolicious plugin allowing customization to force file download
